，間接可以遊客感受到呢場革命嘅氣氛<br />\n<br />\n地鐵: 警隊最近改變策略想洗白，唔方便入地鐵站捉人<br />\n<br />\n好多手足都諗到去地鐵客户服務排隊<br />\n買飛去抗衡呢個戇撚柒鳩嘅禁制令<br />\n與其你搞港鐵，點解唔直接去機場？<br />\n<br />\n當每個人都拎住行李篋入機場排晒大隊<br />\n而政府又冇合理理由驅散你哋嘅時候<br />\n呢個行動就一定比地鐵淨坐eye catching <br />\n<br />\n我唔係想分化，亦都明白各有各做<br />\n但希望各位搞活動嘅手足明白到一個星期得三日係最多人行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n點可以揸實政府個袋，大家都明嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n另外唔好再講咁禁唔禁制令<br />\n大家仲係咁聽話嘅話<br />\n遲啲喺地鐵裝埋啲大陸式嘅安檢<br />\n係咪仲會接受到呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfnUdMq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfnUdMq.jpg&h=54b5048d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DOdTujM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDOdTujM.jpg&h=1fd0e3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家我哋缺乏嘅就係一個明確嘅時間一齊去機場<br />\n希望大家可以盡快有一個共識<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警林鄭，屌你老母</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:18:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bd4d5ee8ca66fdccbb9006024383d2008dd83b0","tid":1498461,"uid":72800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:18:37.000Z","msg":"'If not us, <strong>WHO</strong>? <br />\nIf not now, <strong>WHEN</strong>?'<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">RIGHT THE WRONG, FREE HONG KONG</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em>毋忘六烈 八百義 兩眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n過期毒氣 元朗黑夜 811警暴 雙肺 一裙 無數屈辱私刑<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n試問誰還未發聲<br />\n都捨我其誰<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>衛我城</strong></span><br />\n天生有權還有心可作主<br />\n誰要認命噤聲[/center]<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmfE8Gr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmfE8Gr.jpg&h=24d31a61&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\